        <link rel = "stylesheet" href = "coding challenge stle.css">
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="page-content">
        <header>
            <nav class="navbar">
                <h1 class = "logo">Raqun's Collection</h1>
                <ul class ="nav-links">
                    <li><a href = "#about">About</a></li>
                    <li><a href = "#artworks">Artworks</a></li>
                    <li><a href = "#tools">Tools</a></li>
                    <li><a href = "#contact">Contact</a></li>
                </ul>
                <input type="checkbox" id="dark-toggle">
                <label for="dark-toggle" class="toggle-label">
                    <span class="toggle-ball"></span>
                </label>
            </nav>
            
            <div class = "hero">
                <h2>A Quant Gallery</h2>
                <p>Character-inspired digital illustrations I've made throughout the years</p>

                <a href = "#gallery" class = "btn">View Gallery</a>
            </div>
        </header>

        <section id="about" class ="section">
            <h2>About the Artist</h2>
            <p>
                Hi! I'm Starstruckraqun, or Raqun for short. I'm a digital artist that loves drawing fanart inspired by the little creative flashes of thoughts in my head.
            </p>
        </section>
        
        <section id = "gallery" class = "section">
            <h2>Featured Artworks</h2>
            <div class = "project-container">
                <div class = "project-card">
                    <img src="YURI WEDDING flipped.png" alt = "Alice and Yuzuha Wedding">
                    <h3>Spring Wedding</h3>
                    <p>
                        Alice and Yuzuha's wedding that I drew after being inspired by their story interactions in game. 
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class = "project-card">
                    <img src = "kim dokja died_darker.png" alt="Kim Dokja Sleeping">
                    <h3>After a Long Shift</h3>
                    <p>I was very sleep deprived at this time, and instead of sleeping I decided to let one of my favorite characters sleep for me.</p>
                </div>

                <div class = "project-card">
                    <img src = "Hunkaliscious.png" alt = "Competitive Boxer Mydei">
                    <h3>Competitive Boxing</h3>
                    <p>I watched the Korean bl show MIGNON, I enjoyed it, and I was inspired to draw Mydei, a character from Honkai Star Rail, as a boxer.</p>
                </div>

                <div class = "project-card">
                    <img src="IMG_3892 (1).PNG" alt = "Do I Look Like Him?">
                    <h3>Do I Look Like Him?</h3>
                    <p>I was not well during Durin's story quest. I loved the parallels between him and Wanderer, as much as it breaks my heart.</p>
                </div>

                <div class = "project-card">
                    <img src = "sunday one.png" alt = "Sunday">
                    <h3>Fallen Halovian</h3>
                    <p>I loved Sunday's story line so much, i decided to draw him.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="project-card">
                    <img src ="Jabber art trade.png" alt="Jabber Art Trade">
                    <h3>Baby's First Art Trade</h3>
                    <p>An art trade I did with @sntrylm in Tiktok. It was very fun to draw Jabber, I'm glad I had the change to.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="tools" class = "section">
            <h2>My Tools & Mediums</h2>
            
            <div class="skills-container">
                <span>Krita</span>
                <span>Procreate</span>
                <span>Rendering Methods</span>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="contact" class ="section">
            <h2>Contact</h2>
            <p>Email: starstruckraqun@gmail.com</p>
            <p>Instagram: @starstruckraqun</p>
            <p>Tiktok: @starstruckraqun</p>
            <p>X: @starstruckraqun</p>
            <p>Tumblr: @starstruckraqun</p>
            <a href ="#" class="btn">Commission Info</a>
        </section>

